Title: Prestonpans
Writer: Diana Gabaldon (based on the series of books written by), Ronald D. Moore (developed by), Ira Steven Behr (written for television by)
Actors: Caitriona Balfe, Sam Heughan, Duncan Lacroix, Graham McTavish
Plot: Jamie needs to bypass a swamp to lead the Jacobite army to win over the British army in a critical battle. Benefiting from her experience as a combat nurse during WWII, Claire tends to wounded and dying warriors.
